import sys

n = int(sys.stdin.readline().strip())
a = [int(x) for x in sys.stdin.readline().strip().split()]
t = [int(x) for x in sys.stdin.readline().strip().split()]

ans = 0
for i in range(n):
    ans += a[i] * t[i]

print(ans)

#!/usr/bin/env python3

import sys
